<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">
          <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
            <span>3</span>
            <span>4</span>
          </span>
          &divide;
          <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
            <span>4</span>
            <span>7</span>
          </span>
          를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </span>
              &divide;
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>7</span>
              </span>
              를 계산하려면 먼저 무엇을 해야 할지 생각해 보세요.
            </h3>
            <div class="speech_bubble">
              <div class="bubble_txt">
                분모가 다를 때에는<br>어떻게 하지?
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                    <p>통분하여 분모를 같게 만들어야 합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </span>
              &divide;
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>7</span>
              </span>
              를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
            </h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="21"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span class="f32b">28</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="16"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span class="f32b">28</span>
              </span>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="21"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="16"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(21)/(16)"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="1(5)/(16)"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">분모가 다른 (분수)&divide;(분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                    <p>통분한 다음 분자끼리 나누어 계산합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
